1
00:01:33,620 --> 00:01:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome!</font>

2
00:01:35,750 --> 00:01:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every time I pass by here, 
I smell such lovely flowers!</font>

3
00:01:39,810 --> 00:01:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been so curious!</font>

4
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As have I.</font>

5
00:01:42,980 --> 00:01:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san, please pick 
a flower you like.</font>

6
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:48,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I'm allowed to pick?!</font>

7
00:01:48,620 --> 00:01:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course.</font>

8
00:01:51,030 --> 00:01:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will it be?</font>

9
00:01:52,690 --> 00:01:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-How about... roses?</font>

10
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:58,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We happen to have wonderful roses today.</font>

11
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

12
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, then... we'll take three.</font>

13
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

14
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darling, wrap these up!</font>

15
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing, honey.</font>

16
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}They'll be taking these.</font>

17
00:02:12,790 --> 00:02:14,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}He's a big guy!</i></font>

18
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sure.{bg}</font>

19
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}He sounds like he's high up...</i></font>

20
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you married?</font>

21
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I'm human, 
and my husband is an oni.</font>

22
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have an interspecies marriage.</font>

23
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}An interspecies marriage... 
and we're an interspecies couple...</i></font>

24
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}YAKO - TONOME</font>

25
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. You're the one who always 
stops in front of our shop, right?</font>

26
00:02:34,770 --> 00:02:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry I never come in...</font>

27
00:02:37,780 --> 00:02:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, it's fine. We're 
happy you stopped by today.</font>

28
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you are.</font>

29
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The baby's breath is on the house.</font>

30
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, thank you!</font>

31
00:02:47,990 --> 00:02:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}It's amazing that he can wrap 
flowers with those huge hands...</i></font>

32
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where in the office shall I place them?</font>

33
00:02:55,690 --> 00:02:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to see.</font>

34
00:02:57,870 --> 00:02:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for coming!</font>

35
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe on the table?</font>

36
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, because it's the center of the room!</font>

37
00:03:10,190 --> 00:03:14,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The office is instantly transformed 
into a healing space!</font>

38
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That reminds me. 
Have you always liked roses?</font>

39
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:19,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well...</font>

40
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've taken a liking to them 
since you gave me one, Akira-san.</font>

41
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can say the most incredible 
things off the cuff, Shizuka-san.</font>

42
00:03:32,610 --> 00:03:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, let's put them on the table, then.</font>

43
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course!</font>

44
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What just happened?!</font>

45
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry!</font>

46
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:54,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because I kicked the tree.</font>

47
00:03:55,670 --> 00:03:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sure it's not.</font>

48
00:03:58,080 --> 00:04:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't make a sound like 
that just by kicking a tree.</font>

49
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

50
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you tell from the horn?</font>

51
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're from a species with horns?</font>

52
00:04:08,860 --> 00:04:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I actually can't see.</font>

53
00:04:11,970 --> 00:04:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that explains that.</font>

54
00:04:14,740 --> 00:04:17,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold out your hand. I'll help you up.</font>

55
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:19,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

56
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're very strong, aren't you? 
Thank you for your help.</font>

57
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm an oni-human mix.</font>

58
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oni are strong, but I'm still pretty bad 
at controlling my strength.</font>

59
00:04:33,610 --> 00:04:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I ask why it is 
that you kicked a tree?</font>

60
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:39,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was feeling frustrated.</font>

61
00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was playing with friends, and...</font>

62
00:04:53,230 --> 00:04:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only meant to tap her, 
but I still go too hard sometimes.</font>

63
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't wanna play if I'm just gonna 
make people cry, so I slipped away.</font>

64
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How cool! Like a lone wolf!</font>

65
00:05:07,380 --> 00:05:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm really not.</font>

66
00:05:09,770 --> 00:05:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't think isolating yourself 
is really a good solution.</font>

67
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... what should I do, then?</font>

68
00:05:20,010 --> 00:05:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see...</font>

69
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:26,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yu! Where have you been?</font>

70
00:05:26,570 --> 00:05:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We looked everywhere!</font>

71
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's her fault for crying and say 
she didn't wanna play with you, right?</font>

72
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Yu's fault!</font>

73
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, he made you skin your knee...</font>

74
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Listen...</font>

75
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about we use this?</font>

76
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A cattail?</font>

77
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tag you with it and not hurt you.</font>

78
00:05:46,380 --> 00:05:47,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Like this.</font>

79
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

80
00:05:49,900 --> 00:05:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess that's okay.</font>

81
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'd help with my claws, too.</font>

82
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all use them for the game!</font>

83
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it'll be hard to notice 
we've been tagged with those.</font>

84
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

85
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about making bundles?</font>

86
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:05,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I've got rubber bands!</font>

87
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back!</font>

88
00:06:09,770 --> 00:06:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home!</font>

89
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just can't get a handle on it.</font>

90
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up, Tonome-chan?</font>

91
00:06:18,890 --> 00:06:21,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, it's that guy again!</font>

92
00:06:21,140 --> 00:06:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, my client believes 
someone's smuggling</font>

93
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">their product to sell 
on the black market.</font>

94
00:06:26,710 --> 00:06:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's one of the suspects.</font>

95
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, hey! Did my curse come in handy?</font>

96
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, he didn't do anything 
suspicious that day.</font>

97
00:06:36,290 --> 00:06:37,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it didn't matter at all?!</font>

98
00:06:40,020 --> 00:06:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me!</font>

99
00:06:42,350 --> 00:06:44,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome. Is that you, Yu-kun?</font>

100
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! Hi, Yako-oneechan!</font>

101
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello!</font>

102
00:06:48,230 --> 00:06:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Thanks for having me today!{bg}</font>

103
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's all this?</font>

104
00:06:49,330 --> 00:06:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's interviewing us about our jobs. 
For school, apparently.</font>

105
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yes.</font>

106
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We run an agency, 
so let me introduce you to the staff.</font>

107
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's someone you know?</font>

108
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the son of a florist 
couple we've gotten to know.</font>

109
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

110
00:06:58,280 --> 00:07:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonome-san, this is Yu Kemauchi. 
He'll be learning about our office today.</font>

111
00:07:03,050 --> 00:07:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you!</font>

112
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a pleasure.</font>

113
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:09,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Tonome, the head detective here.</font>

114
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something the matter?</font>

115
00:07:11,590 --> 00:07:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

116
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinking I've seen this guy.</font>

117
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have?</font>

118
00:07:16,570 --> 00:07:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

119
00:07:17,350 --> 00:07:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was playing with my friends</font>

120
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he yelled at me like, 
"You can't be here!"</font>

121
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was it a dangerous area?</font>

122
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember where you were?</font>

123
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

124
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. This area, eh?</font>

125
00:07:29,990 --> 00:07:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}So what kind of job do 
you do, Yako-oneechan?{bg}</font>

126
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, most likely.</font>

127
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:38,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I handle the office finances 
and manage everyone's schedules.{bg}</font>

128
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll scope it out.</font>

129
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we catch him 
in the act, we've got him.</font>

130
00:07:36,930 --> 00:07:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't it be dangerous?</font>

131
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll arrange an escort.</font>

132
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yako-san.</font>

133
00:07:42,210 --> 00:07:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm heading out.</font>

134
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care!</font>

135
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, are they going to the place I said?</font>

136
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't say!</font>

137
00:07:55,950 --> 00:07:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yako-oneechan, thanks for the interview.</font>

138
00:07:59,260 --> 00:08:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that all you needed?</font>

139
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure Jarashi-san will be 
back any minute now...</font>

140
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:05,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, it's fine.</font>

141
00:08:05,110 --> 00:08:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm heading home.</font>

142
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:07,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later!</font>

143
00:08:20,030 --> 00:08:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I'm gonna tail this detective!</i></font>

144
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}It's my chance to see what 
the job's really about!</i></font>

145
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I'll get a great report out of this!</i></font>

146
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I know. I'll get pics too!</i></font>

147
00:08:31,420 --> 00:08:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? He's gone!</font>

148
00:08:34,350 --> 00:08:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just lost sight of him for a second!</font>

149
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the...</font>

150
00:08:41,610 --> 00:08:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Was that Yu-kun?</i></font>

151
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I sensed someone following me...</i></font>

152
00:08:46,100 --> 00:08:48,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I didn't think he'd come after me.</i></font>

153
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}That's not safe. I'll get some 
distance and change my route there.</i></font>

154
00:08:56,190 --> 00:08:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Now, then...</i></font>

155
00:08:57,950 --> 00:08:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}So it's somewhere around there?</i></font>

156
00:09:04,180 --> 00:09:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}How much are we shipping?</font>

157
00:09:05,810 --> 00:09:07,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Too much at once'll be suspicious.</font>

158
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We'll have to break it up.</font>

159
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}When's payment?{bg}</font>

160
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}There he is.</i></font>

161
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}After receipt. I'll hand it 
over after it checks out.{bg}</font>

162
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}That must be the group he's selling to.</i></font>

163
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I want one lump sum at the end.{bg}</font>

164
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}This is my chance 
to catch him in the act.</i></font>

165
00:09:15,180 --> 00:09:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Got it.{bg}</font>

166
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:19,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The shift changes today 
are evening and late night.{bg}</font>

167
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What the hell are you doing?!</font>

168
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Slippery little brat...</font>

169
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mere!</font>

170
00:09:23,930 --> 00:09:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I wasn't doing anything! 
I was just looking for something!</font>

171
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't do anything wrong!</font>

172
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This little brat 
was taking pictures of us!</font>

173
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}{M}Y-Yu-kun...</i></font>

174
00:09:32,460 --> 00:09:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sneaking around the area, too.</font>

175
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't doing anything!</font>

176
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, we can't let those pics get out.</font>

177
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just remembered!</font>

178
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was hanging around here
yesterday as well!</font>

179
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, someone send you to spy on us?</font>

180
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

181
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:52,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This little brat's pretty strong...</font>

182
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, he's an oni. Be careful.</font>

183
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}That's right. If I struggle 
too much, I could hurt them!</i></font>

184
00:10:01,250 --> 00:10:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, he settled down.</font>

185
00:10:03,070 --> 00:10:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take his phone and lock 
him in the back room.</font>

186
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, now.</font>

187
00:10:11,090 --> 00:10:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I deleted the pics 
on his phone. What now?</font>

188
00:10:13,830 --> 00:10:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's contact the execs for now.</font>

189
00:10:15,930 --> 00:10:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What about the boss?{bg}</font>

190
00:10:16,890 --> 00:10:18,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He'll be here soon.{bg}</font>

191
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:20,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is getting out of control.{bg}</font>

192
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}What do I do? What's 
going to happen to me?</i></font>

193
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Well, what can you do?{bg}</font>

194
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can sell this kid for good money!</font>

195
00:10:26,860 --> 00:10:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, let's throw him 
in the ocean so he can't tell no one!</font>

196
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up! Quit crying!</font>

197
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:36,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pipe down already!</font>

198
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:40,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

199
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:47,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to worry. I've called for backup.</font>

200
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you a little bit of myself.</font>

201
00:10:54,130 --> 00:10:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

202
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}S-So cool!</i></font>

203
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I can't see him, but...</i></font>

204
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Maybe I'll be a detective when I grow up!</i></font>

205
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, this ain't great.</font>

206
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right? We should probably 
pass on the word...</font>

207
00:11:16,050 --> 00:11:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

208
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? Well, we've got 
a little situation here...</font>

209
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll untie you now.</font>

210
00:11:27,530 --> 00:11:28,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

211
00:11:29,900 --> 00:11:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So?</font>

212
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say leave the kid and move shop.</font>

213
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

214
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, hurry it up!</font>

215
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing.</font>

216
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darn it. What a pain in my neck...</font>

217
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's dark!</font>

218
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:50,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we do? I can't see anything.</font>

219
00:11:50,690 --> 00:11:52,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wait just a minute.</font>

220
00:11:52,940 --> 00:11:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness.</font>

221
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I'm glad the detective is here.</i></font>

222
00:11:57,940 --> 00:11:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}He's like a superhero!</i></font>

223
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what made you want to 
become a detective?</font>

224
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:07,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well...</font>

225
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:11,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A long time ago, something happened. 
I wanted someone to find me.</font>

226
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But nobody was able to, 
and it made me very sad.</font>

227
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I became a detective to find 
other people who want to be found.</font>

228
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:28,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it! And that's why you found me, too!</font>

229
00:12:29,470 --> 00:12:31,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm getting a call.</font>

230
00:12:31,110 --> 00:12:31,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

231
00:12:33,050 --> 00:12:34,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Akira-san?</i></font>

232
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

233
00:12:36,470 --> 00:12:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've made it in, and I'm with Yu-kun.</i></font>

234
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yu-kun?!</font>

235
00:12:40,060 --> 00:12:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he all right?</font>

236
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:43,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes. He wasn't harmed.</i></font>

237
00:12:43,770 --> 00:12:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness!</font>

238
00:12:46,530 --> 00:12:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say...</font>

239
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:48,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes?</i></font>

240
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could you keep talking to me?</i></font>

241
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just to... distract me.</i></font>

242
00:12:55,530 --> 00:12:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, then...</font>

243
00:12:57,120 --> 00:13:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long, long ago, in a land far away...</font>

244
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why a fairy tale?!</font>

245
00:13:01,330 --> 00:13:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's not easy to just keep talking!</font>

246
00:13:05,210 --> 00:13:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, sorry. A fairy tale is fine.</i></font>

247
00:13:08,070 --> 00:13:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll start over, then.</font>

248
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long, long ago, in a land far away,</font>

249
00:13:14,190 --> 00:13:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there lived an old woman and an old man.</font>

250
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:19,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The old man went to punch the mountain.</font>

251
00:13:19,050 --> 00:13:20,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Take that!</font>

252
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The old woman went 
to the river to race a peach.</font>

253
00:13:24,740 --> 00:13:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You can't keep up with me!</font>

254
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those two sound like they're 
in rather good health.</font>

255
00:13:30,330 --> 00:13:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The peach was their victory prize.</font>

256
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For what?!</font>

257
00:13:34,290 --> 00:13:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Yako.</font>

258
00:13:35,250 --> 00:13:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right!</font>

259
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:42,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I forgot to mention it, but Jarashi-san 
and Karma-san just arrived!</i></font>

260
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we check on the kid?</font>

261
00:13:46,190 --> 00:13:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah.</font>

262
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the stuff on the second floor?</font>

263
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're getting it down now.</font>

264
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

265
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What are you doing?!</font>

266
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just feel so weak...</font>

267
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with you?</font>

268
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno! It just hit me.</font>

269
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, let's hurry.</font>

270
00:14:09,100 --> 00:14:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do we do?</font>

271
00:14:10,010 --> 00:14:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I head out ahead 
once we've got a full load?</font>

272
00:14:12,270 --> 00:14:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, please do.</font>

273
00:14:13,460 --> 00:14:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

274
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kikira, is the tracker working?</font>

275
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah.</i></font>

276
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

277
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can hunt down these 
child kidnappers myself?</font>

278
00:14:27,910 --> 00:14:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, just keep it under control.</font>

279
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just get it finished.</font>

280
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, before the truck comes backâ€”</font>

281
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who're you?</font>

282
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you give yourselves up quietly...</font>

283
00:14:50,820 --> 00:14:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm willing to show mercy.</font>

284
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:55,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crap. The jig's up.</font>

285
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, is that how we're doing it?</font>

286
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No mercy needed, then?</font>

287
00:15:09,570 --> 00:15:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn!</font>

288
00:15:10,190 --> 00:15:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You okay?!</font>

289
00:15:11,010 --> 00:15:12,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, you...!</font>

290
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-S-Sorry! Forgive me! Mercy, please!</font>

291
00:15:32,210 --> 00:15:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pathetic.</font>

292
00:15:34,230 --> 00:15:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you wanted to apologize, 
you shouldn't have started with me.</font>

293
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said you could give 
yourselves up quietly.</font>

294
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:45,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really thought I'd 
apologize, you brute?!</font>

295
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell do embezzlers have guns?!</font>

296
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch it! Watch it!</font>

297
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:54,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take that and that and that and that!</font>

298
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die!</font>

299
00:16:07,590 --> 00:16:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wasting my damn time.</font>

300
00:16:11,500 --> 00:16:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There we go.</font>

301
00:16:15,450 --> 00:16:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wait up!</font>

302
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just sit still!</font>

303
00:16:21,390 --> 00:16:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Catch me if you can! So long!</font>

304
00:16:24,290 --> 00:16:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not going anywhere!</font>

305
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Takes some guts to try to escape me.</font>

306
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dummy!</font>

307
00:16:34,880 --> 00:16:35,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stop it!</i></font>

308
00:16:39,970 --> 00:16:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told her to keep it under control.</font>

309
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The light's on!</font>

310
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found you!</font>

311
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hurt, kiddo? You cry?</font>

312
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine! And I didn't cry!</font>

313
00:16:51,880 --> 00:16:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For reals?</font>

314
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Jarashi-san?</font>

315
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:56,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She beat the crap outta the bad guys.</font>

316
00:17:06,990 --> 00:17:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome!</font>

317
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll tie him up. Go get Jarashi-san.</font>

318
00:17:10,810 --> 00:17:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yessir!</font>

319
00:17:13,930 --> 00:17:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just heard quite a sound! 
Are you all right?!</i></font>

320
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

321
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your distraction let me relax 
until I had to spring into action.</font>

322
00:17:21,340 --> 00:17:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your fairy tale was a big help.</i></font>

323
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're welcome!</font>

324
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are Yu-kun and everyone else okay?</i></font>

325
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. We'll all be heading back soon.</font>

326
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roll, acorn, roll. Roll, acorn, roll.</font>

327
00:17:39,820 --> 00:17:44,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, there it goes, right into the lake...</font>

328
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

329
00:17:45,790 --> 00:17:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which way was it again?</font>

330
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's... the moon?</font>

331
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:13,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you just say something?</font>

332
00:18:13,990 --> 00:18:18,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah... Why am I lying on your lap?</font>

333
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:24,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suggested it, since you seemed tired 
from everything today.</font>

334
00:18:24,950 --> 00:18:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come along! Everyone's 
gone home, so let's indulge!</font>

335
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always wanted to 
be someone's pillow!</font>

336
00:18:33,210 --> 00:18:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, just for a while.</font>

337
00:18:36,100 --> 00:18:38,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long was I asleep?</font>

338
00:18:38,390 --> 00:18:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About fifteen minutes, I think?</font>

339
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you just... kiss me? 
That was very sudden...</font>

340
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Was that... what I've only read 
about in romance novels...</i></font>

341
00:19:12,330 --> 00:19:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}A real grown-up kiss?!</i></font>

342
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Akira-san...</font>

343
00:19:20,140 --> 00:19:23,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you by my side forever.</font>

344
00:19:23,710 --> 00:19:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aki...</font>

345
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I feel the same way.</font>

346
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good evening!
Tonome-san!</font>

347
00:19:36,670 --> 00:19:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eh?</font>

348
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What is it?</font>

349
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:46,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much 
for helping my son today!</font>

350
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

351
00:19:46,110 --> 00:19:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, not at all!</font>

352
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Yu! You have 
something to say, right?</font>

353
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

354
00:19:50,050 --> 00:19:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry for causing 
you trouble today!</font>

355
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. I appreciate your help...</font>

356
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're very sorry to intrude.</font>

357
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you didn't!</font>

358
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll leave our gift to you outside!</font>

359
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right.</font>

360
00:20:07,630 --> 00:20:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Let's go home.</font>

361
00:20:09,570 --> 00:20:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

362
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've become like regulars at this bar!</font>

363
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have been here quite a few times.</font>

364
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first time we came, 
I imploded on alcohol a little, but...</font>

365
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no romantic experience!</font>

366
00:20:39,380 --> 00:20:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought that was charming, though.</font>

367
00:20:41,120 --> 00:20:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wipe it from your memory.</font>

368
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, when I first 
invited you on a date,</font>

369
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:49,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there was something 
that worried me, too.</font>

370
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I'm older, and I'm your boss...</font>

371
00:20:54,410 --> 00:20:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you might feel like you 
couldn't say no. That I coerced you.</font>

372
00:20:58,360 --> 00:21:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I absolutely didn't!</font>

373
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I realize now that 
it was an unfounded fear.</font>

374
00:21:03,280 --> 00:21:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It certainly was!</font>

375
00:21:05,790 --> 00:21:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I've felt like 
the childish one around you lately.</font>

376
00:21:09,710 --> 00:21:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't! You've 
helped me out a lot, too...</font>

377
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean... I want us to be 
able to rely on each other.</font>

378
00:21:20,690 --> 00:21:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. So...</font>

379
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to make it official.</font>

380
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Official?</font>

381
00:21:26,890 --> 00:21:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not that I haven't thought 
about it before, but...</font>

382
00:21:30,570 --> 00:21:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san.</font>

383
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like us to date with 
the goal of marriage.</font>

384
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marriage?!</font>

385
00:21:38,570 --> 00:21:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that a problem?</font>

386
00:21:40,010 --> 00:21:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not a problem!</font>

387
00:21:42,570 --> 00:21:44,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want us to get married! We <i>will</i>!</font>

388
00:21:44,900 --> 00:21:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, not just yet.</font>

389
00:21:45,890 --> 00:21:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We <i>won't</i>!</font>

390
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You answered so quickly.</font>

391
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not nervous anymore, at least.</font>

392
00:21:54,330 --> 00:21:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I want it to always 
be your hand that's guiding me.</font>

393
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, shall we make plans to cohabit?</font>

394
00:22:03,170 --> 00:22:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're cohabiting?!</font>

395
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just yet.</font>

396
00:22:06,970 --> 00:22:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 7: I WANT YOU BY MY SIDE</font>

397
00:22:07,190 --> 00:22:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But let's start planning for it.</font>

